data.meta_description: Located 48 km / 30 miles to the north-east of London on the M11 motorway, London Stansted Airport (STN) is the country's third-busiest airport and around the 50th in the world.  Stansted Airport serves almost 24 million passengers annually, travelling to some 150 destinations worldwide in 35 different countries.
